data.description: Home, sweet home! Nestled on a desirable corner lot, this move-in ready, 4-bed, 2-bath property boasts a 3-car garage and a welcoming front porch. Inside, find a combined living/dining room with high ceilings, a fresh cool palette, and a mix of wood-look and tile flooring. The great room is ideal for intimate gatherings with loved ones. The kitchen comes with a cozy breakfast nook, granite counters, cabinets with crown molding, a tile backsplash, SS appliances, pendant/recessed lighting, a handy pantry, and an island with a breakfast bar. Double doors lead to the main bedroom, complete with an ensuite with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. Grab your favorite drink and relax on the screened patio for year-round enjoyment. Make it yours today!
